The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                               IN THE CITY
                        
	 The Indian Oil-Bengal Table Tennis Association summer coaching camp will be held at the Khudiram Anushilan Kendra from May 27. 150 young table tennis aspirants will be trained during the one-month long camp.                 
	 Mohun Bagan player PC Lalawmpuiya has confirmed his move to the Chirag United SC for the coming season. Another Bagan player, Lalkamal Bhowmik, was in advanced negotiations with the same club. Chirag were also said to be interested in Surojit Roy of Mahindra United.                 
	SOCCER: The Telegraph Cup at the CCFC                                                                                                                                                                       
